{"tid":2400111,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深水埗再被封 警員忘形狂奔跑過龍 鄧炳強「快閃」即走懶理記者提問","createTime":"2021-02-08T15:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T04:27:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9420d3ee0c63b8e0626ac45b17aee08aad8cc694","tid":2400111,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:59:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-_TjdyhWrxQ&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-_TjdyhWrxQ%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=79ac0321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-_TjdyhWrxQ&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/run_1.jpg?itok=Ejbm1Fx0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2Frun_1.jpg%3Fitok%3DEjbm1Fx0&h=482a2642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒報導）政府連續第八晚「遍地封區」，先後第九次突襲油尖旺區及第二次突襲深水埗區。警員圍封深水埗恆安樓時，一度狂奔百米，發現「跑過龍」後才突然掉頭。警務處長鄧炳強至晚上10時45分才到場視察，惟一如官員既往不回應記者和市民的做法，「快閃」7分鐘後即離開。<br />\n<br />\n繼佐敦渡船角文英樓於晚上7時被圍封後，深水埗恆安樓亦於晚上8時30分被劃入「受限區域」。晚上8時24分（政府發出封區公告前6分鐘），有警員「偷步」於恆安樓門外貼上通告。期間，一名警員突然向深水埗地鐵站D2出口方向忘形狂奔，其餘十多名警員亦尾隨奔跑，衝刺近100米至桂林街與福華街交界時，警員顯得猶豫，方才突然轉身跑回恆安樓附近，並拉起封鎖線。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080731&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=eeda3668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080731&h=d52a1686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080731</a>"},{"pid":"9730d734a76abda2e4f999b7f2a7d112bb48a586","tid":2400111,"uid":183844,"like":77,"dislike":1,"score":76,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:04:02.000Z","msg":"啲狗係咁<br />\n放風開心得濟"},{"pid":"d31745de2ae1f